Na4.} 10. e4 c5 {Unleashing the bishop on b7 and allowing for easy development.
} 11. d5 {e5 is more common but can be comfortably met by Nd5} exd5 12. e5 Ne4
{This is the most accurate.} 13. Nxd5 c4 {Nxe5 is interesting, but after
